CB Bank]] while [[Britannia]], [[BIG FM 92.7]], [[Mountain Dew]], [[Kingfisher (beer)|Kingfisher Premium]], Bookmyshow, [[Punjab Kesari]], [[The Tribune (Chandigarh)|The Tribune]], Blippar, [[Smile Foundation]], Trip Factory and [[AIDS Healthcare Foundation]] function as their partners.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kxip.in/official-sponsors-partners/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=11 April 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408053001/http://kxip.in/official-sponsors-partners/ |archive-date=8 April 2015 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|- \n! style=\"width:1%;background:#D30816; color:#E6E6FA;\"|Year\n! style=\"width:13%;background:#D30816; color:#E6E6FA;\"|Kit Manufacturers\n! style=\"width:13%;background:#D30816; color:#E6E6FA;\"|Shirt Sponsor (Front) \n! style=\"width:13%;background:#D30816; color:#E6E6FA;\"|Shirt Sponsor (Back) \n! style=\"width:13%;background:#D30816; color:#E6E6FA;\"|Chest Branding\n|-\n|2008\n|rowspan=4|[[Reebok]]\n|[[Spice Digital|Spice]] \n|[[Kotak Mahindra Bank|Kotak]] \n|[[Provogue]]\n|-\n|2009\n|rowspan=3|[[Fly Emirates]]\n|[[7 UP|7 Up Nimbooz]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Gulf Oil]]\n|-\n|2010\n|[[Mountain Dew]]\n|-\n|2011\n|Pearls\n|[[Linc Pen & Plastics Limited|Linc Pens]]\n|-\n|2012\n|[[U.S. Polo Assn.]]\n|[[Videocon d2h]] \n|rowspan=2|[[Lux Cozi]] \n|[[U.S. Polo Assn.]]\n|-\n|2013\n|rowspan=\"5\" |[[TYKA Sports]]\n|NVD Solar\n|NVD Solar\n|-\n|2014\n|rowspan=3|[[Tata Prima|Tata Motors Prima]]\n|[[Arise India|Arise Mobiles]] \n|Trip Factory\n|-\n|2015\n|[[Mankind Pharma|Manforce]]\n|[[HTC]]\n|-\n|2016\n|rowspan=2|[[Idea Cellular|Idea]]\n|[[Ashland Inc.|Valvoline]]\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Hero Cycles]]\n|[[Philkeram Johnson|Johnson]]\n|-\n|2018\n|rowspan=3|T10 Sports\n|[[Kent RO Systems]]\n|[[Jio]]\n|Lotus Herbals\n|-\n|2019\n|[[Aaj Tak]]\n|Bageshree Lake City\n|rowspan=2|[[Jio]]\n|-\n|2020\n|EbixCash\n|\n|}\n\n==Statistics==\n{{see also|List of Kings XI Punjab records}}\n\n===